<exercise id="fs-id1641348">
<problem id="fs-id1990386"><para id="fs-id1990387">Which of the following cells is important in the innate immune response?</para>
<list id="fs-id1471448" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>B cells</item>
<item>T cells</item>
<item>macrophages</item>
<item>plasma cells</item>
