<exercise id="fs-id1865619">
<problem id="fs-id1421217"><para id="fs-id1547027">Which of the following cells would be most active in early, antiviral immune responses the first time one is exposed to pathogen?</para>
<list id="fs-id2370321" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
